{
  "stem": "22391.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's really what, what happened, because the trains weren't going.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So there were a whole bunch of people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It wasn't myself.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then they had the soup kitchens in between in different cities that they were looking for people like we were.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they were feeding us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there are-- there were the one who told me, well, if you go here, you could go that far.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "If you go there, you, you know-- nobody really know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were all--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--refugees, and nobody really knows what really was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not at all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, I, I couldn't speak to them, so I couldn't really, you know, relate with them at all.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was just-- did meet the refugees themselves.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was plenty around in everywhere.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And true-- at night, they, they didn't really let you walk through the border, but there was a couple of them who know how to go back and forth.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were taking us back and forth to go there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So then finally I got to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there, too, the trains weren't moving.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I didn't have no money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I went also to another soup kitchen where they-- all the refugees were gathering.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they told me to wait for a certain time, and a horse and buggy comes from one town to the other town, and you could go with them.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went with them, and then I had a very bad experience there, because I had a loose thing in my hand.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was hardly anything that I took with me, but they give me conserve, what the Americans were getting from them to eat-- what did they call that?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The little conserve food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was cheese in that, and all kinds-- K-rations?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's what it was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's what I had.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
